======================================================================
NAME
----------------------------------------------------------------------

lib-tree

======================================================================


======================================================================
VERSION
----------------------------------------------------------------------

0.01 - This is the initial version.

======================================================================


======================================================================
DEPENDENCIES
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Test::More
Config
Carp
File::Spec
File::Spec::Functions
File::Path
Cwd

======================================================================


======================================================================
INSTALLATION
----------------------------------------------------------------------

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Install, you can use the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

======================================================================


======================================================================
SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION
----------------------------------------------------------------------

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc lib::tree

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=lib-tree

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/lib-tree

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/lib-tree

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/lib-tree/

